        "text": "Needham married the biochemist [[Dorothy M. Needham]] (1896–1987) in 1924 and they became the first husband and wife both to be elected as [[Fellows of the Royal Society]] - [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joseph_Needham#Personal_life wikipedia]"
